{
  "texts": [
    "In Fig. 3, a comparison of the number of VR-related papers is shown alongside those that also include biosensors.",
    "In the graph, the grey line represents the total number of papers that included the term \"Virtual Reality\" in their research per year.",
    "The two dashed lines depict the percentage of all articles that included VR in their research and utilized VR and biosensors: the total of VR&BS papers (% VR&BS total) is represented by the dashed green line, and those analyzed in this review (% iVR&BS analyzed) are represented by the dashed orange line.",
    "As outlined in Fig. 3, the numbers of papers on general VR experiences and biosensors is increasing.",
    "Less costly HMDs may explain this academic interest, and deepfer interest in this type of technology."
  ]
}